A new documentary is being released showcasing&nbsp; African Entrepreneurs. At the 2015 edition of DEMO Africa, 30 of the best and most innovative African start-ups made the final list from an applicant pool of over 600 startups to pitch at the two day competition.&nbsp;"Venture: An Entrepreneur's Journey" welcomes viewers into the entrepreneurial journey of four of the winners from the continent to Silicon Valley. DEMO Africa is a flagship initiative of LIONS@FRICA, a continent-wide venture launch-pad that provides the most innovative African companies with a platform to present their products to the global ecosystem. Read more.&nbsp;